{
  "text": "The state-of-the-art equipment, namely, multicollector inductively coupled plasma mass spectrometer (MC-ICP-MS) and isotope ratio mass spectrometer (IRMS), were used to determine coffee authenticity and its origin [CITATION_1] О 2 isotope were determined in the samples. The measurement results showed a high degree authenticity of coffee origin, especially for countries in South America.",
